job_description:
We are seeking a Civil Engineer with a strong background in structural design and transportation infrastructure. 
The ideal candidate will have experience working with AutoCAD, performing site inspections, and leading mid-sized construction projects. 
Knowledge of government regulations and permitting processes is a must. A PE license is preferred.
